Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Never opposites when we play the same {\c&H2208CF&}game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:28.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,We walk a thin line between {\c&H2208CF&}hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:30.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Running from the {\c&H2208CF&}truth{\r} but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Told so many {\c&H2208CF&}lies{\r} I don't know if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Only one {\c&H2208CF&}life{\r} to live so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Heads{\r} or {\c&H2208CF&}tails{\r}? do you know what side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Does it even matter if it's on the same coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,If you wanna achieve you gotta {\c&H2208CF&}believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,The time is right now there's the door here's the {\c&H2208CF&}keys{\r}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Just gotta chase the pain away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,let it fade away
